      <title>消息人士称，李小龙电影制片厂正在考虑出售新加坡电影院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/bruce-lee-film-studio-is-said-to-weigh-sale-of-singapore-cinemas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，橙天嘉禾娱乐控股有限公司正在考虑出售其在新加坡和台湾的电影院，并寻求至少 4 亿美元的资产估值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/bruce-lee-film-studio-is-said-to-weigh-sale-of-singapore-cinemas</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:33:58 GMT</pubDate>
